description: Coefficients in expansion of Dirichlet series Product_p (1 - (Kronecker(m,p) + 1)*p^(-s) + Kronecker(m,p)*p^(-2s))^(-1) for m = 25.
comments: Number of divisors of n not congruent to 0 mod 5.
formula: Multiplicative with a(5^e)=1 and a(p^e)=e+1 for p<>5.Moebius transform is period 5 sequence [ 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, ...]. - _Michael Somos_, Oct 31 2006
maple: for n from 1 to 500 do a := ifactors(n):s := 1:for k from 1 to nops(a[2]) do p := a[2][k][1]:e := a[2][k][2]: if p=5 then b := 1:else b := e+1:fi:s := s*b:od:printf(`%d,`,s); od:
prog: (PARI) {a(n)=if(n<1, 0, sumdiv(n, d, d%5>0))} /* _Michael Somos_, Oct 31 2006 */(PARI) {a(n)=if(n<1, 0, direuler(p=2, n, 1/(1-X)/if(p==5, 1, 1-X))[n])} /* _Michael Somos_, Oct 31 2006 */
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
